# Environment Variables — Mika

Copy to `.env` and fill in values. **Never commit `.env` to git.**

```bash
# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://mika:changeme@localhost:5433/mika

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Telegram
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your-bot-token-from-botfather
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_SECRET=random-secret-string

# Auth
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-random-64-chars
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=change-me-to-another-random-64-chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# Encryption (AES-256 — generate with: openssl rand -hex 32)
ENCRYPTION_KEY=your-64-char-hex-key

# App
NODE_ENV=development
API_PORT=3001
WEB_PORT=3000
TZ=America/Sao_Paulo

# Frontend
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Routines (n8n cron → API)
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
ROUTINE_API_KEY=your-routine-api-key-here
```
